product_desc:
Gooru has developed an open, flexible web-based platform which helps teachers share high quality resources and personalize instruction for their students. Using a crowd-sourced model, we enable K-12 teachers to create and contribute playlists of Common Core-aligned web resources so students can learn every topic their way. Gooru also provides tools to remix content and track student progress with data analytics, so teachers can intervene in real-time and adapt the learning experience to support students at every level. Our free and open-source technology is comprised of the following key components: 
-a catalog, with over 16 million multimedia resources, questions, and collections;
-a community of inspiring educators, public schools, charter schools, and other organizations, who contribute their content and expertise;
-and analytics, which helps teachers get insight into the specific kind of support each student needs so they can provide real-time intervention or instant feedback.

iospedisco.it is the first italian parcel delivery comparison website that helps you to compare costs and services of the leading national and international couriers, easily and for free. Through a easy-to-use platform you have access to the rates of selected carriers ( ex.: UPS, BRT,etc) and you can purchase the solution that best suits to your needs. 
By using iospediso.it private customers and companies (in particular e-commerce) have the following advantages:
+ Saving: up to 70% of shipments' costs thanks to the lowest rates in the market;
+ Transparency: services are sorted by price (all inclusive), delivery time and quality (users rank couriers on 3 variables: kindness, punctuality and reliability);
+ Simplicity: a unique user-friendly private area to manage all carriers, documents and tracking;
+ Support: a single point of contact in a click to handle all couriers and a team of professionals is always available.

 www.iospedisco.it

